          <h4 className="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight">Zainstaluj aplikację</h4>
          <p className="text-xs text-gray-500">Kliknij <span className="inline-block"><svg className="w-4 h-4 mx-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth="2" d="M8.684 13.342C8.886 12.938 9 12.482 9 12c0-.482-.114-.938-.316-1.342m0 2.684a3 3 0 110-2.684m0 2.684l6.632 3.316m-6.632-6l6.632-3.316m0 0a3 3 0 105.367-2.684 3 3 0 00-5.367 2.684zm0 9.316a3 3 0 105.368 2.684 3 3 0 00-5.368-2.684z" /></svg></span> a potem „Do ekranu początkowego”</p>
